1. *Iskrena* ispovest me je oslobodila tereta. (The *honest* confession freed me from the burden.)
2. Ona je *iskrenu* zahvalnost izrazila kada sam joj pomogao. (She expressed *sincere* gratitude when I helped her.)
3. Kada si *iskren*, ljudi te više cene. (When you are *honest*, people appreciate you more.)
4. Njena *iskrenost* je privukla mnoge ljude u njen život. (Her *sincerity* has attracted many people into her life.)
5. *Iskreno* govoreći, ne znam šta bih učinio u toj situaciji. (To be *honest*, I don't know what I would do in that situation.)
6. Ona je bila *iskrena* u svojim namerama, ali nije uspela da ispuni obećanje. (She was *genuine* in her intentions, but failed to keep her promise.)
7. Molim te, budi *iskren* i reci mi istinu. (Please be *truthful* and tell me the truth.)
8. Njegove *iskrene* reči su me dirnule. (His *sincere* words touched me.)
9. *Iskrenim* osmehom je pozdravila svakog gosta koji je ulazio. (She greeted every guest with a *genuine* smile.)
10. *Iskrenost* je vrlina koju cenim kod ljudi. (Sincerity is a virtue that I value in people.)